    public static interface ReadBaseStratification.RecordAndOffsetStratifier<T extends java.lang.Comparable<T>>
    The main interface for a stratifier. The Stratifier needs to be able to ake a RecordAndOffset and return a value of type T. It also needs to have a suffix for automatically generating metrics file suffixes.
